@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/engine

### 1. NQM 엔진 연결 (ID: 0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "NQM",
  "id": 0
}

### 2. Anhua 엔진 연결 (ID: 1, IP 지정)
POST {{baseUrl}}/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "Anhua",
  "id": 1,
  "ip": "192.168.0.100",
  "port": 5000
}

### 3. 0번 엔진(NQM) 상태 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/0/status

### 4. 1번 엔진(Anhua) LED 켜기
POST {{baseUrl}}/1/led?isOn=true